definition: abbr. for 藝術學校|艺术学校/art school

sentences.english: Do I quit and go to art school?
sentences.chinese: 還是我應該辭職去藝校學習？

sentences.english: Oh, to know the next one art school, on the other side in the triple.
sentences.chinese: 呵呵，在下知道一個藝校，就在三聯那邊。

sentences.english: Interviews candidates apply for the Department of Fashion Show, lined up in front of art school.
sentences.chinese: 面試，報考服裝表演系的考生，在藝校門前排起長隊。
